### 把下面的 roomId / userId 換成你查到的實際 id(99999 那條故意不換)

### 1. 成功 → 預期 201
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{"roomId":1,"userId":1,"startTime":"2026-07-01T10:00:00","endTime":"2026-07-01T11:00:00","subject":"Test Meeting","purpose":"demo","attendeeCount":5}

### 2. 衝突 → 預期 409(跟上面一模一樣再送一次)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{"roomId":1,"userId":1,"startTime":"2026-07-01T10:00:00","endTime":"2026-07-01T11:00:00","subject":"Test Meeting","purpose":"demo","attendeeCount":5}

### 3. 查無會議室 → 預期 404
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{"roomId":99999,"userId":1,"startTime":"2026-07-01T14:00:00","endTime":"2026-07-01T15:00:00","subject":"x","attendeeCount":2}

### 4. 格式錯(缺 subject、attendeeCount=0)→ 預期 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{"roomId":1,"userId":1,"startTime":"2026-07-01T16:00:00","endTime":"2026-07-01T17:00:00","attendeeCount":0}
